{"id":283,"parent_id":277,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":283,"title":"2 Samuel 6","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Sam.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 6"],[".studySummary",["i","David takes the ark to the city of David—Uzzah is smitten for steadying the ark and dies—David dances before the Lord, causing a breach between him and Michal."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.1","order":"02.11.006.22701"},["b","1"],"Again, David",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"gathered"],"together all",["i","the"],"chosen",["i","men"],"of Israel, thirty thousand."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.2","order":"02.11.006.22702"},["b","2"],"And David arose, and went with all the people that",["i","were"],"with him from Baale of Judah, to bring up from thence the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"ark"],"of God, whose name is called by the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts that dwelleth",["i","between"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"cherubims"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.3","order":"02.11.006.22703"},["b","3"],"And they set the ark of God upon a new cart, and brought it out of the house of Abinadab that",["i","was"],"in Gibeah: and Uzzah and Ahio, the sons of Abinadab, drave the new cart."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.4","order":"02.11.006.22704"},["b","4"],"And they brought it out of the house of Abinadab which",["i","was"],"at Gibeah, accompanying the ark of God: and Ahio went before the ark."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.5","order":"02.11.006.22705"},["b","5"],"And David and all the house of Israel played before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"on all manner of",["i","instruments made of"],"fir wood, even on",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"harps"],", and on psalteries, and on timbrels, and on cornets, and on cymbals."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.6","order":"02.11.006.22706"},["b","6"],"¶And when they came to Nachon’s threshingfloor, Uzzah put forth",["i","his hand"],"to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"ark"],"of God, and took hold of it; for the oxen shook",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.7","order":"02.11.006.22707"},["b","7"],"And the anger of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was kindled against",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Uzzah"],"; and God",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"smote"],"him there for",["i","his"],"error; and there he died by the ark of God."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.8","order":"02.11.006.22708"},["b","8"],"And David was displeased, because the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had made a breach upon Uzzah: and he called the name of the place",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Perez-uzzah"],"to this day."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.9","order":"02.11.006.22709"},["b","9"],"And David was afraid of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that day, and said, How shall the ark of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"come to me?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.10","order":"02.11.006.22710"},["b","10"],"So David would not remove the ark of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"unto him into the city of David: but David carried it aside into the house of Obed-edom the Gittite."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.11","order":"02.11.006.22711"},["b","11"],"And the ark of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"continued in the house of Obed-edom the Gittite three months: and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"blessed Obed-edom, and all his household."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.12","order":"02.11.006.22712"},["b","12"],"¶And it was told king David, saying, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath blessed the house of Obed-edom, and all that",["i","pertaineth"],"unto him, because of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"ark"],"of God. So David went and brought up the ark of God from the house of Obed-edom into the city of David with gladness."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.13","order":"02.11.006.22713"},["b","13"],"And it was",["i","so,"],"that when they that bare the ark of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had gone six paces, he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sacrificed"],"oxen and fatlings."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.14","order":"02.11.006.22714"},["b","14"],"And David",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"danced"],"before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"with all",["i","his"],"might; and David",["i","was"],"girded with a linen ephod."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.15","order":"02.11.006.22715"},["b","15"],"So David and all the house of Israel brought up the ark of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"with shouting, and with the sound of the trumpet."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.16","order":"02.11.006.22716"},["b","16"],"And as the ark of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came into the city of David, Michal Saul’s daughter looked through a window, and saw king David leaping and dancing before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and she despised him in her heart."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.17","order":"02.11.006.22717"},["b","17"],"¶And they brought in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"ark"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and set it in his place, in the midst of the tabernacle that David had pitched for it: and David offered burnt offerings and peace offerings before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.18","order":"02.11.006.22718"},["b","18"],"And as soon as David had made an end of offering burnt offerings and peace offerings, he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"blessed"],"the people in the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.19","order":"02.11.006.22719"},["b","19"],"And he dealt among all the people,",["i","even"],"among the whole multitude of Israel, as well to the women as men, to every one a cake of bread, and a good piece",["i","of flesh,"],"and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"a flagon",["i","of wine"]],["i","."],"So all the people departed every one to his house."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.20","order":"02.11.006.22720"},["b","20"],"¶Then David returned to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"bless"],"his household. And",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"Michal"],"the daughter of Saul came out to meet David, and said, How glorious was the king of Israel to day, who",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"uncovered"],"himself to day in the eyes of the handmaids of his servants, as one of the vain fellows shamelessly uncovereth himself!"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.21","order":"02.11.006.22721"},["b","21"],"And David said unto Michal,",["i","It was"],"before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", which chose me before thy father, and before all his house, to appoint me ruler over the people of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", over Israel: therefore will I play before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.22","order":"02.11.006.22722"},["b","22"],"And I will yet be more vile than thus, and will be base in mine own sight: and of the maidservants which thou hast spoken of, of them shall I be had in honour."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.23","order":"02.11.006.22723"},["b","23"],"Therefore Michal the daughter of Saul had no child unto the day of her death."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.1a","order":"02.11.006.22724"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.5"},"1 Chr. 13:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.2a","order":"02.11.006.22726"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/13.13.6-14"},"1 Chr. 13:13 (6–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.2b","order":"02.11.006.22728"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cherubim"},"TG Cherubim"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.5a","order":"02.11.006.22730"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/31.27"},"Gen. 31:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/15.16"},"1 Chr. 15:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/3.5.5,7,10,15"},"Dan. 3:5 (5, 7, 10, 15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.6a","order":"02.11.006.22732"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/85.8"},"D&C 85:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.7a","order":"02.11.006.22734"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/15.2"},"1 Chr. 15:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.7b","order":"02.11.006.22736"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/1.51"},"Num. 1:51"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/6.19"},"1 Sam. 6:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.8a","order":"02.11.006.22738"},["b","8a"],["span.small","IE"],"Breach of Uzzah."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.12a","order":"02.11.006.22740"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ark-of-the-covenant"},"TG Ark of the Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.13a","order":"02.11.006.22742"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/15.26.25-28"},"1 Chr. 15:26 (25–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.14a","order":"02.11.006.22744"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.28"},"D&C 136:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.17a","order":"02.11.006.22746"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/3.15"},"1 Kgs. 3:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.18a","order":"02.11.006.22748"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.14.14-15"},"1 Kgs. 8:14 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/16.2"},"1 Chr. 16:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.19a","order":"02.11.006.22750"},["b","19a"],["span.small","HEB"],"(perhaps) a raisin-cake."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.20a","order":"02.11.006.22752"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/16.43"},"1 Chr. 16:43"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.20b","order":"02.11.006.22754"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/14.49"},"1 Sam. 14:49"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/6.20c","order":"02.11.006.22756"},["b","20c"],["span.small","IE"],"In his joyful dancing, more of his body was exposed than she believed proper."]]}
